{"tid":1381052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"退休警員用他人身份證　盜竊等罪成立判囚3年10個月","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T12:45:39.000Z","uid":275588,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"804afb93504ae49b454ff0fea956425e83ec8cbe","tid":1381052,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:06:58.000Z","msg":"一名因屢次犯事而被勒令提早退休的六旬警員，聲稱因在深圳賭錢輸了，欠款約30萬，被人威嚇下去年初使用他人身份證，向銀行表示要更改密碼、提款、甚至取出定期存款等，偷取共約657萬元，他從中獲取一成得益。<br />\n被告今日在區域法院因盜竊及串謀盜竊等5項罪名，被判入獄3年10個月。<br />\n法官判刑時說，被告有計劃地犯案，即使可能不是案中主腦，但亦扮演重要角色。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471131-20190729.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471131-20190729.htm&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=d0985ec6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471131-20190729.htm&h=4ea1979d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471131-20190729.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5f182facec2d08b5ee8e7bf932f5a676159de62a","tid":1381052,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:10:40.000Z","msg":"又係佔中"},{"pid":"db8b189a247ec465318faa3c028ef058378909f7","tid":1381052,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806ddcd8e9ded637e8bebe8f10ac24b062912df1","tid":1381052,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:45:39.000Z","msg":"他從中獲取一成得益<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /